nd modes available at launch |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130930125516/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/09/27/battlefield-4-announces-the-full-list-of-maps-and-modes-available-at-launch/ |archive-date=September 30, 2013 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Release date\">{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/05/22/battlefield-4-release-date-announced-for-early-november/ |title= Battlefield 4 release date announced, will arrive late October/early November |date= May 22, 2013 |accessdate= May 22, 2013 |first= Phil |last= Savage |publisher= [[PC Gamer]] |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130607144544/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/05/22/battlefield-4-release-date-announced-for-early-november/ |archive-date= June 7, 2013 |url-status= live |df= mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Release date for Europe\">{{cite web |url=http://www.game.co.uk/en/battlefield-4-with-premium-expansion-pack-216110 |title=Battlefield 4 release date for EU November 1 |publisher=Game |accessdate=August 15, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091932/http://www.game.co.uk/en/battlefield-4-with-premium-expansion-pack-216110 |archive-date=March 4, 2016 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Release date in New Zealand\">{{cite web|url=https://help.ea.com/article/battlefield-4-worldwide-release-schedule|title=Battlefield 4 Worldwide Release Schedule|publisher=Electronic Arts|accessdate=October 27, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031090249/http://help.ea.com/article/battlefield-4-worldwide-release-schedule|archive-date=October 31, 2013|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"retrailer gamespot\">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/battlefield-4-retailer-image-shows-october-31-release-6407526 |work=gamespot.com |title=Battlefield 4 retailer image shows October 31 release |publisher=[[GameSpot]] |date=April 25, 2013 |accessdate=April 26, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130427112133/