ntury Indian women politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian politicians]]\n[[Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians]]\n[[Category:Chief ministers from Bharatiya Janata Party]]\n[[Category:Chief Ministers of Delhi]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cardiac arrest]]\n[[Category:Female foreign ministers]]\n[[Category:Health ministers of India]]\n[[Category:Women chief ministers of Indian states]]\n[[Category:Indian women lawyers]]\n[[Category:Janata Party politicians]]\n[[Category:Leaders of the Opposition (India)]]\n[[Category:Lok Sabha members from Delhi]]\n[[Category:Lok Sabha members from Madhya Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Ministers for External Affairs of India]]\n[[Category:Ministers for Information and Broadcasting of India]]\n[[Category:Panjab University alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Ambala]]\n[[Category:People from Delhi]]\n[[Category:Punjabi people]]\n[[Category:Rajya Sabha members from Haryana]]\n[[Category:Rajya Sabha members from Uttarakhand]]\n[[Category:State cabinet ministers of Haryana]]\n[[Category:Women members of the Cabinet of India]]\n[[Category:Women in Delhi politics]]\n[[Category:Women in Haryana politics]]\n[[Category:Rajya Sabha members from Madhya Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Indian women diplomats]]\n[[Category:Members of the National Cadet Corps (India)]]\n[[Category:Narendra Modi ministry]]\n[[Category:Indian Hindus]]\n[[Category:State funerals in India]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Padma Vibhushan in public affairs]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Indian politician}}\n{{EngvarB|date=April 2017}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| name = Sushma Swaraj\n| office = [[Ministry of External Affairs (India)|Minister of External Affairs]]\n| image = Sushma Swaraj Ji.jpg\n| caption = Sushma Swaraj in 2018\n| predecessor = [[Salman Khurshid]]\n| primeminister = [[Narendra Modi]]\n| successor = [[Subrahmanyam Jaishankar]]\n| office2 = [[Leader of the Opposition (India)|Leader of the Opposition in the Lok Sabha]]\n| pred